{"id":231824043,"title":"【威士忌】絕版18年Bunnahabhain","content":"https://i.imgur.com/qTgw1ti.jpg\n\n這支酒目前已經絕版,新版的是一個年輕的船長掌舵,猜測應該是舊的品酒師已經退休,新任品酒師上任才換圖案\n\n香氣:\n釋放出蜂蜜堅果味、細緻的皮革味、豐富的果香,\n會感受到濃郁太妃糖及強韌的橡木香氣。\n\n口感:\n停留在嘴裡時,因為是老酒想對的辛辣感不會那麼重,這款強調的也不是泥煤味,而是他豐富的層次。前期我可以喝到淡淡的泥煤味,到了中期會是橡木與皮革的味道,而最後的尾韻是豐富的果香,像是頻果跟鳳梨等水果的濃厚的香味。另外這款威士忌尾韻可以拉很長,非常的黏舌,如果是喜愛雪莉桶的同好這款有機會一定要喝看看\n\n他還有另一個兄弟,被稱為“美麗的錯誤”,有人能夠猜出來我說得是誰嗎","excerpt":"這支酒目前已經絕版，新版的是一個年輕的船長掌舵，猜測應該是舊的品酒師已經退休，新任品酒師上任才換圖案，香氣：釋放出蜂蜜堅果味、細緻的皮革味、豐富的果香，會感受到濃郁太妃糖及強韌的橡木香氣。口感：停留在","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"23082c2f-c19d-456c-a805-1e6ac0a36c31","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-08-09T07:40:02.349Z","updatedAt":"2019-08-09T07:40:02.349Z","commentCount":4,"likeCount":12,"tags":[],"topics":["品酒板","威士忌"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"品酒","forumAlias":"alcohol","school":"中山醫學大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":11},{"id":"011ead16-9b83-4729-9fde-c588920c6c2d","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/qTgw1ti.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"d1f4990d-6c5c-44d0-8f82-2193634ced19","url":"https://i.imgur.com/qTgw1til.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/qTgw1til.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/qTgw1til.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-08-09T07:40:02.349Z","updatedAt":"2019-08-09T07:40:02.349Z"},{"id":"d1f4990d-6c5c-44d0-8f82-2193634ced19","url":"https://i.imgur.com/qTgw1ti.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/qTgw1ti","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/qTgw1til.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-08-09T07:40:02.349Z","updatedAt":"2019-08-09T07:40:02.349Z"}],"postAvatar":""}